"# 04 - Domain Adaptation Demonstration (Stress Recovery)\n",
"\n",
"This notebook demonstrates how to apply unsupervised domain adaptation techniques to the stressed data (Target Domain) to recover the performance of the baseline EEGNet decoder. We will implement the CORAL (Correlation Alignment) loss to minimize the domain discrepancy between the clean (Source) and stressed (Target) feature distributions."
]
